        "如果同时安装 OpenJS.NodeJS 的多个版本，会相互覆盖，仅保留最高版本"
    ],
    "architecture": {
        "64bit": {
            "url": "https://nodejs.org/dist/v25.2.1/node-v25.2.1-x64.msi#/dl.msi_",
            "hash": "4e16e4f3e761bc1242ab4f4f191b3f570cb498e31f3d6f14e01caf0db2573c22"
        },
        "arm64": {
            "url": "https://nodejs.org/dist/v25.2.1/node-v25.2.1-arm64.msi#/dl.msi_",
